    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301000/extras/2fa40c881aed81630c611ed2c3404328.avif?t=1772127570\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301000/extras_big/2fa40c881aed81630c611ed2c3404328.avif?t=1772127570 width=800 height=138 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以自己的节奏探索浩瀚白境</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏上一段无尽雪山的旅程，在这款独立滑雪冒险中，探索与故事完美融合。手持滑雪板，你将穿越壮丽的高山地形，发现隐藏的路径、令人叹为观止的美景，以及山脉的秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开放世界滑雪</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越广袤的开放式山脉，自由选择路径，滑过冰封山峰、茂密森林和幽静山谷。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301000/extras/a83f36647c5fb8e2a30198fac74f2918.poster.avif?t=1772127570\" width=480 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301000/extras/a83f36647c5fb8e2a30198fac74f2918.webm?t=1772127570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301000/extras/a83f36647c5fb8e2a30198fac74f2918.mp4?t=1772127570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>发现隐藏的秘密</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索山脉的每一个角落，找到隐藏的路线和壮丽的景观，揭示山脉的历史。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>结识山间的居民</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在旅途中，你会遇到其他探险者、睿智的当地人和神秘的陌生人。他们或许会与你分享故事、交给你任务，或者透露值得一探的隐秘地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好探索<strong>浩瀚白境</strong>了吗？拿起你的滑雪板，以全新的方式征服这座山脉吧！</p>",
